         <div xml:id="bHY6yh-d43978"><!-- p2l6-r12 -->
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d43978-Hd1e108">Rubrica 12</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d43978-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De obedientia et contumacia</head>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d43978-d1e114">
               <lb ed="#V" n="26"/>¶ De audientia et contumacia. Rubrica. 12.
    </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d43978-d1e119">
               <lb ed="#V" n="27"/>
               <ref><sic>MOises</sic> in deuteronomio
      <lb ed="#V" n="28"/>c. 5.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d43978-Qd1e125">Non declina
        <lb ed="#V" n="29" break="no"/>bis neque dexteram neque ad sinistram
        <lb ed="#V" n="30"/>sed per viam quam praecepit dominus deus
        <lb ed="#V" n="31"/>ambulabitis vt viuatis: et bene sit vobis: et <!--'u' in "bene" flipped-->
        <lb ed="#V" n="32"/>protelentur dies vestri in terra possessionis vestre.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d43978-d1e137">
               <lb ed="#V" n="33"/>
               <ref>Salomon in prouerbiis. c. 15.<ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d43978-Qd1e141">Mens iu
        <lb ed="#V" n="34" break="no"/>sti meditatur obedientiam.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d43978-d1e148">
               <lb ed="#V" n="35"/> /
               <ref>Idem in eccl. c. 4.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d43978-Qd1e152">Multo melior est obe
        <lb ed="#V" n="36" break="no"/>dientia quam stultorum victime.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d43978-d1e158">
               <lb ed="#V" n="37"/>
             ¶ <ref>Regum li. i. c. 15.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d43978-Qd1e162">Melior est obedientia
        <lb ed="#V" n="38"/>quam victime.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d43978-d1e168">
               <lb ed="#V" n="39"/>
             ¶ <ref>Terentius in phormione. ca. 4.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d43978-Qd1e172">Inscitia
        <lb ed="#V" n="40"/>est aduersus stimulum calces.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d43978-d1e178">
               <lb ed="#V" n="41"/>
             ¶ <ref>Uirgilius eneid. li. 4. ante medium.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d43978-Qd1e182">Ocius
        <lb ed="#V" n="42"/>omnes Imperio leti parent: ac iussa facessunt.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d43978-d1e188">
               <lb ed="#V" n="43"/>
             ¶ <ref>Tullius de legibus li. 3.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d43978-Qd1e192">Qui imperat pa
        <lb ed="#V" n="44" break="no"/>ruerit aliquoniam necesse est: et qui modeste paret <!--142.xml-->
        <cb ed="#V" n="b"/>
                  <lb ed="#V" n="45"/>videtur quod aliquoniam imperet dignus esse.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d43978-d1e204">
               <lb ed="#V" n="46"/>
             ¶ <ref>Petrus apostolus epistola. i.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d43978-Qd1e208">Subditi estote omni hu
        <lb ed="#V" n="47" break="no"/>mane creature proptur deum: siue regi quasi precellen
        <lb ed="#V" n="48" break="no"/>ti: siue ducibus tanquam ab eo missis: ad vindi
        <lb ed="#V" n="49" break="no"/>ctam malefactorum: laudem vero bonorum. Adole
        <lb ed="#V" n="50" break="no"/>scentes subditi estote senioribus.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d43978-d1e221">
               <lb ed="#V" n="51"/>
             ¶ <ref>Lucas in actibus apostolorum. c. 9.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="52"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d43978-Qd1e225">Durum est contra stimulum calcitrare.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d43978-d1e231">
               <lb ed="#V" n="53"/>
             ¶ <ref>Paulus apostolus: epistola ad romanos. c. 13</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="54"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d43978-Qd1e235">Omnis anima potestatibus sublimioribus subdita sit
        <lb ed="#V" n="55"/>Qui resistit potestati: dei ordinationi resistit</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d43978-d1e243">
               <lb ed="#V" n="56"/>
             ¶ <ref>Seneca tragediarum in medea. c. 4.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d43978-Qd1e247">Equum
        <lb ed="#V" n="57"/>atque iniquum regis imperium feras.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d43978-d1e253">
               <lb ed="#V" n="58"/>
             ¶ <ref>Cato. c. i.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d43978-Qd1e257">Foro pare.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d43978-d1e261">
               <lb ed="#V" n="59"/>
             ¶ <ref>Cassiodorus epistolarum li. 2. epistola. 12</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="60"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d43978-Qd1e265">Imperium si in paruo contenitur: in omni par
        <lb ed="#V" n="61" break="no"/>te violatur.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d43978-d1e273"> /
               <ref>Li. 11 e. 9.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d43978-Qd1e275">Odium sibi excitat quae
        <lb ed="#V" n="62"/>iustis resultat imperiis.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d43978-d1e282">
               <lb ed="#V" n="63"/>
             ¶ <ref>Prouerb. vulgar:</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d43978-Qd1e286">El no e seno repenare
        <lb ed="#V" n="64"/>alaseio.
        <lb ed="#V" n="65"/>Lo tutti eguale deo vol male.</quote>
            </p>
